               <msContents>
                  <summary>F<locus target="#1r">fols. 1r, </locus>-152r: Psalter, Dawit, ዳዊት፡ The midpoint is marked with the center strophe written in alternating black and red letters. Psalm 151 is the long version. Song of Songs is the common version. F. i v-ii r: undeciphered text giving many names. <locus target="#138v">138v, </locus>: Note of secondary ownership, ቄስ ገብረ ስላሴ, written in purple ink. Praises of Mary begins on Monday and culminates in Sunday. <locus target="#152r">152r, </locus>, right column-152v: an undeciphered geneology, written in blue ink, mentioning several times a Däjazmač. <locus target="#153r">153r, </locus>: Another Geneological text, written in light blue ink. <locus target="#153v">153v</locus>: The complete fedel, alphabet in the seven orders. </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
